    <item>
      <title>१५ अहम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/15_aham/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/15_aham/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;THE MEANING OF THE WORD AHAM (1) IN THE SECOND HALF OF THE ŚLOKA                  [[page587]]&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Español&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;EL SIGNIFICADO DE LA PALABRA AHAM (1)&lt;br&gt;&#xA;EN LA SEGUNDA MITAD DEL ŚLOKA [[587]]&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;परयजन-वशष&#34;&gt;प्रयोजन-विशेषः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इव्व् इडत्तिल् ‘‘मोक्षयिष्यामि’’ ऎऩ्गिऱ उत्तमऩाले &amp;ldquo;नाऩ्&amp;rdquo; ऎऩ्ऱु तोऱ्ऱानिऱ्क,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;नीलमेघः (सं)&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अत्र &amp;ldquo;मोक्षयिष्यामि&amp;rdquo; इत्य् उत्तमेन&#xA;&amp;ldquo;अहम्&amp;rdquo; इति प्रतीयमाने ऽपि&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here from the first person singular, mokṣayiṣyāmi (I will set Thee free),&lt;br&gt;&#xA;(from this) itself, the meaning &amp;lsquo;I&amp;rsquo; &lt;strong&gt;is&lt;/strong&gt; evident.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>१६ त्वा</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/16_tvA/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/16_tvA/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;THE MEANING OF THE WORD TVĀ (THEE) :  page588&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Español&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;EL SIGNIFICADO DE LA PALABRA TVĀ (TI): página 588&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;तततव-तरय-ववक&#34;&gt;तत्त्व-त्रय-विवेकः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;‘‘त्वा’’ ऎऩ्ऱदु&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;‘‘न त्वेवाहं’’&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;मुदलाऩ उपदेश-परंपरैयाले चिद्-अचिद्-ईश्वर-तत्त्व-त्रय-विवेकम् पिऱन्दु&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;नीलमेघः (सं)&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;त्वा&amp;rdquo; इत्य् अनेनोच्यते,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;न त्वेवाहम्&amp;rdquo; इत्य्-आरभ्योपदेश-परम्-परया&lt;br&gt;&#xA;चिद्-अचिद्-ईश्वर-तत्त्व-त्रय-विवेके जाते&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The word tvā (Thee) means:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Thou that &lt;strong&gt;hast acquired&lt;/strong&gt; the power of &lt;strong&gt;discrimination&lt;/strong&gt; (viveka)&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;necessary&lt;/strong&gt; to &lt;strong&gt;understand&lt;/strong&gt; the (nature of the) three tattvas (reals) viz., cit, acit and Iśvara,&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>१७ सर्व-पापेभ्यः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/17_sarva-pApebhyaH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/09_pAda-3/17_sarva-pApebhyaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;सङगत&#34;&gt;सङ्गतिः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;THE MEANINGS OF SARVA PĀPEBHYO (FROM ALL SINS) : page589&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Español&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;LOS SIGNIFICADOS DE SARVA PĀPEBHYO (DE TODOS LOS PECADOS): página 589&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इप्-पडि बन्ध-मोक्ष-शक्तऩ् आऩ मोक्ष-प्रदऩैयुम्;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;अ-शक्तऩ् आय्, अवऩ् पक्कलिले न्यस्त-भरऩ् आऩ मुमुक्षुवैयुञ्&lt;br&gt;&#xA;जॊल्लि,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;नीलमेघः (सं)&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इत्थं बन्ध-मोक्ष-शक्तं मोक्ष-प्रदम्,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;अ-शक्तं तत्-सन्निधौ न्यस्त-भरं मुमुक्षुं च&lt;br&gt;&#xA;उक्त्वा&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Having thus &lt;strong&gt;referred&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;to the &lt;strong&gt;Dispenser&lt;/strong&gt; of mukti&lt;br&gt;&#xA;who &lt;strong&gt;is capable&lt;/strong&gt; of &lt;strong&gt;putting&lt;/strong&gt; the jīva in &lt;strong&gt;bondage&lt;/strong&gt; or out of it&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
